Citation.sTitle: Viscosities, Densities, and Ultrasonic Velocities of Binary Mixtures of Ethylbenzene with Ethanol, 1-Propanol, and 1-Butanol at (298.15 and 308.15)K
Citation.sAbstract: The viscosities, densities, and ultrasonic velocities of binary mixtures of ethylbenzene with ethanol, 1-propanol, and 1-butanol have been determined at 298.15 and 308.15 K over the whole composition range. Excess compressibility () and deviations in viscosity () were evaluated and presented as functions of composition.
